thread.title: barbara
thread.title_full: Bake Me A Wish! reviewed by barbara

author: barbara
title: barbara
text:
It was part of a birthday present and it arrived on time. It was
packed so well you'd think I was receiving a kidney!!!
I ordered the samples (eclairs, Napoleons,etc) and they
tasted like they were just baked in someone's kitchen So
good.
Drawback...maybe because I spent all my life (up until three
weeks ago) in the city and we always had lots of bakeries around
that I compared the expense and I thought it was kind of pricey.
I think back and perhaps because of the packing and shipping. Will I order from here again...yes I will.
